\subsection{symmetry breaking}
\begin{frame}
\visible{
\begin{textblock}{16}(0,2)
\centering
If SUSY was unbroken, superpartner would have same mass\\
we should see them\visible<2>{, but dont! $\rightarrow$ SUSY is broken\\}
\includegraphics[width=.45\textwidth]{src/exactsusysm.png}~
\visible<2>{\includegraphics[width=.45\textwidth]{src/mssm1.png}}\\
